# Decision Log (example)

This is an example how you can have an automatically generated decision log from the ADRs in this folder.
We use Liquid script to generate the tables below from the ADRs.
{% comment -%}
Looping through all the files and show the display name.
The date is extracted from the filename and used in the title.
We also sort on the date and group by year.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign sortedList = current.Files | sort: "Name" | reverse -%}
{%- assign counter = sortedList.size -%}
{%- assign lastYear = 0 -%}
{%- for file in sortedList -%}
{%- assign year = file.Name | slice: 0,4 -%}
{%- assign dt = file.Name | split: '-' | slice: 0,3 | join: "-"  -%}
{%- if year != lastYear %}
## {{ year }}

| # | Date | File | Decision |
| --- | --- | --- |
{%- assign lastYear = year %}
{% endif -%}
{%- if file.IsMarkdown -%}
| {{ counter }} | {{ dt }} | [{{ file.Name }}]({{ file.Name }}) | {{ file.DisplayName }} |
{% endif %}
{%- assign counter = counter | minus: 1 -%}
{%- endfor -%}